70
00:13:42.180 --> 00:13:51.640
Pelle Krabbenhoeft: N plus 1, N plus 2, and N plus 3 slots, and see how many transactions got included on-chain, and you'll see the day in just one second.

71
00:13:52.490 --> 00:13:59.320
